metadata.name: Whispers of Witchcraft 5/5
metadata.description: A Whisper of Witchcraft - sometimes its just a cool breeze or a whisper on the wind. The spirits of the dead wrongfully accused of many things or just mean spirits at play. Beware of the Whispers of Witchcraft. These are the first set of five pieces of art for this series created by DoctorWu aka Randy Monteith
